        <section id="about">
            <h2>About</h2>
            <p>Bhutan, the Kingdom of the Thunder Dragon, is a land of breathtaking natural beauty, rich culture, and ancient traditions. Nestled in the Himalayas, Bhutan offers serene landscapes, historic monasteries, and a unique way of life centered on Gross National Happiness.</p>
